	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I didn't know anything about configuration mode but I'm not surprised it's absent from the 64M carts. That's why all the fixes are needed. Really is a shame that they would *remove* functionality. Why you would go from having some protection for your Master Bank Register to having none makes no sense. Ofcourse the vast majority of games don't bother it but some certainly do. Donkey Kong Land II if I recall does bother it but the rom is so jam packed I didn't see any safe area to add code to fix it. <br /><br />It'll be nice when eventually someone, perhaps Krikzz, develops a new Gameboy Flash cartridge. Too bad they couldn't have left that critical functionality in the 64M version.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
